reviewText: this is the second time i've ordered this dvd and the second time.it does NOT play.i'm not even going to send this second one back. it's in the trash. you will not hear from me again. i'm VERY disappointed with these products.
Ordered this for a friend of mine. He says it's thee worse quality recorded dvd he'd seen in a long time. I agreeed...

I was a little dissapointed as it seemed to be just a video of different clips of other videos they have done. But it is Sha Na Na so of course I bought it.  Next they need to have Sha Na Na jammies. So if you don't own their Musik Laden video then by all means get this. LOVE Sha Na Na so can't go wrong there.
